quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Taa Siin Miim
  26,2,Kuwakani waa Aayadaha Kitaabka ka yeela arrimaha caddaan
  26,3,Waa intaasoo aad naftaada ku disho (murugo) inaysan rumayn (Xaqa) darteed
  26,4,"Haddii aan doonno, Waxaan kaga soo direynaa calaamo cirka, ay luqumahoodu u hogan lahaayeen"
  26,5,"Oo uga ma yimaado waano (Qur'aan) Raxmaanka isagoo cusub oo is daba jooga, bal waa kuwii ka jeesada"
  26,6,"Marka waxay dhabtii beeniyeen (Xaqa), sidaas darteed wararka waxay ku jees-jeesaan baa dhaqso u imaan doona"
  26,7,"Miyeyna arag dhulka,_intee baan nooc kasta oo wanaagsan aan sababnay inuu ku soo baxo"
  26,8,"Hubaal Waxaa arrinkani ku jira xaqiiq calaamo, mase aha badankoodu kuwo rumeyn doona"
  26,9,"Oo hubaal (Allaah) Rabbigaa xaqiiq waa Awood Badanaha, Naxariista Badan"